Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.05,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,队长 嘉斯坦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.54,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,难不成
