Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:06.98,Default_Sub,Man2,0,0,0,,果然他们也是在战斗中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:10.35,Default_Sub,Man2,0,0,0,,干扰电波真强烈
