Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.85,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里是美国军方宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,美国军方宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:37.83,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,美国军方宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.73,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,我们是联合国基地工作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:43.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,联合国基地人员 你们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.06,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,美国军方宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:48.82,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,美国军方宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.37,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:58.31,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.10,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,鲍勃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.51,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,尼克拉耶夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.31,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.56,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,弗兰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.53,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.87,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.17,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.00,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.56,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.98,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,和罗安的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.98,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这样就全分好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.46,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,他的那份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.93,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,「他」？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.99,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不是也该分他一份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:25.48,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,如果被他觉得地球人很小气就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.88,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没办法 我拿去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.44,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大卫那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.77,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,分析模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.49,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我们的存活率有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.35,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,「我们」是指谁 请重新输入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.63,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.78,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,是食物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.68,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.65,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:03.86,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.48,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,谁要给你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.44,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要吃的话自己捡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:36.20,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你来了之后死了几十人了 几十人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.65,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.00,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不爽的话来打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.25,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我来当你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.78,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,来打一架如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.96,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,来打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:02.43,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你这家伙 你这家伙 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.53,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,谁快去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:15.90,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,大卫 快住手吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:16.90,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:21.14,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,如果你 如果你不来 就不会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.50,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:23.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.93,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.19,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,大卫 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.08,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,住手 大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.79,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么要打他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:44.08,Default_Sub,Eliz,0,0,0,,到底是为什么 亚瑟 为什么不阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:47.67,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们后来才来的 而且又离得这么远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:48.82,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们才不要你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.02,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,才不要你来保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:07.92,Default_Sub,Eliz,0,0,0,,你 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.30,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.21,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你们的星球不会打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:08.59,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这样的话 大卫还真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.29,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你也压抑得过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.54,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.38,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,风暴停了 也讨论了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:37.81,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,接下来就根据讨论出来的结论 一口气前往美国基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.51,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.08,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,从这里出发的话 一下就到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:45.84,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,这里就算是再怎么隐秘 还是会被发现的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:55.72,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,激光枪 能源弹夹两单位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:56.40,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:17:00.57,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,更换枪的口径 换成对人类的标准口径
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:01.36,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.21,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,大家老说枪不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.80,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,但这样就像在杀只虫一样轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:15.97,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.68,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,刚刚眼前亮了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.95,Default_Sub,Man2,0,0,0,,比尔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.19,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.41,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,只是我有些不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.31,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:36.80,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,根据刚才所发射的位置 还有射程的推算 发射位置的误差是20±1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.38,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:49.38,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,躲在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.29,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:10.95,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大卫 到美国军方宇宙基地只剩这一段路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.45,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,只有能到基地的话 我们就能平安地回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:17.60,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,然后就再也看不到那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.19,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,前提是要平安到基地对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我们会平安到基地的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.91,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,所以我们才会选择这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:26.95,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:31.95,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,如果美国基地没事的话 那为什么会在交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.35,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,那小孩说的是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.57,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,到了美国基地就全部知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.93,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,还有这件事的责任问题也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.09,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,鲍勃 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:21.08,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.46,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.15,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,鲍勃 梅受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:25.17,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,你是说梅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.97,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,我们被瞄准了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.88,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,他想杀了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.80,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.43,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,鲍勃 车还能开动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.27,Default_Sub,Bob,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.23,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,好吧 了解了 你们快来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:35.98,Default_Sub,Bob,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.63,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我要把你们一个个都杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.72,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,到底在哪 快给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.33,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,鲍勃 尼克拉耶夫 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.83,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,不好了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.87,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,在哪 给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.49,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,多米利亚 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.29,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,上吧 快把他打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.65,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,可是 对方并没有防备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.68,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,算了 那快把那小鬼打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.22,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,卑鄙的家伙 我来做你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:26.80,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不会再让你得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.93,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我来送你下地狱 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:40.82,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:41.54,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,鲍勃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:42.45,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,尼克拉耶夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.24,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.28,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.66,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,快住手 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.33,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,让他们休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.49,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.00,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,只要过了那座山 就是美国基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.64,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.64,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我会把敌人挡在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.78,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,小鬼 来打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:13.95,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我杀了你那么多同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.27,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,来吧 随便从哪来都行 来打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.40,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,多米利亚 我们一起围攻他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.18,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:32.65,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.99,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,是美国基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:35.14,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没有错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.30,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,对 只要到这里的话就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.92,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,太好了 我们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.76,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们差点被那家伙骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.90,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,哪里有战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:46.75,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.00,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,好像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:53.20,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,如果这是梦的话 还真希望不要醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:59.25,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我也是 平安的到了美国基地 我的心里充满了无限的感慨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:05.88,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,一直追着我们的 对战争的不安 在这一瞬间都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:12.94,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,这时候我突然觉得 地球人并不是那么笨的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:13.64,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:14.56,Default_Sub,Eliz,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:16.36,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:33.25,Default_Sub,Bill,0,0,0,,是核弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:35.25,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:37.55,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:43.58,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:45.38,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:47.43,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:57.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,要把抵抗的人类都杀光 古拉多斯星的人都这么冷血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:01.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,把那些害虫都杀了 也不会有损我们古拉多斯的威名的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:04.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那连自己部下都杀了的你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:08.70,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\c&HEEDEE9&\pos(720,770)}让我活下去
